Package cf.ystapi.jda

Class YSTBuilder

java.lang.Object
cf.ystapi.jda.YSTBuilder
public class YSTBuilder extends Object
How to use:

YSTBuilder yst = new YSTBuilder(JDABuilder.build());

yst.setPrefix("!").setOwner("ID").addCommand(new bot());

DiscordBot dis = yst.build();

Since:
Beta 0.0.0.3
